name: Involuntary ̵D̶o̴p̷p̴e̷l̸g̸a̷n̸g̸e̴r̵ 1
description: ID2021 is a collection of mixed media abstract works that studies the synergy between semi figurative and geometrical motives and unexpected symbiotic abstract cells based in analog ink traces.   The collection portraits unconceivable forms of life that are encountered beyond our physical and spiritual realms  bringing hyper techno-cosmic symbiotic beings to life that travel across the infinite in look of other forms of life to feast and reign on them.  Collectors can DM for uncompressed ver.
